The paper proposes a method for activity recognition using temporal reasoning graphs, which involves analyzing video sequences and exploring temporal relations. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper involves natural language processing (cs.CL) in terms of semantic meaning extraction. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.LG, followed by cs.AI, cs.MM, and cs.CL.
